---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Learn about Runners In Need and our mission to connect runners with extra gear to organizations serving runners in need.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">About Runners In Need</h1>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
      <p>
        Many runners accumulate gear over time &mdash; shoes that were the wrong fit,
        race medals, lightly used apparel. At the same time, countless young athletes
        and community runners train in worn-out shoes or go without proper gear.
      </p>
      <p>
        Runners In Need bridges this gap. We connect organizations that serve runners
        &mdash; school coaches, community running programs, volunteer groups &mdash;
        with donors who have gear to give.
      </p>
      <p>
        Organizers post specific needs with details about sizes, types, and quantities.
        Donors browse, pledge what they can offer, and coordinate delivery. It's simple,
        direct, and makes sure the right gear gets to the right people.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 pt-4">How It Works</h2>
      <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Organizers</strong> sign up and post what their runners need.</li>
        <li><strong>Donors</strong> browse needs by location and category.</li>
        <li><strong>Pledge</strong> gear you want to donate and coordinate delivery.</li>
        <li><strong>Deliver</strong> &mdash; ship it or arrange a local drop-off.</li>
      </ol>

      <div class="pt-6">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Ready to help?</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">
            Browse active needs if you have extra running gear, or apply as an organizer if your program needs support.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-lg bg-[#2D4A2D] px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-[#1F361F] focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-[#2D4A2D]/50 focus-visible:ring-offset-2">
              Browse Needs
            </a>
            <a href="/become-organizer" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-lg border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 hover:border-[#2D4A2D] hover:text-[#2D4A2D] focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-[#2D4A2D]/50 focus-visible:ring-offset-2">
              Become an Organizer
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
